Afro-life star Fireboy DML has been unveiled as brand ambassador for popular phone brand, Tecno. The YBNL artiste was unveiled ambassador for ‘Spark’ by Tecno Nigeria via their Instagram page. Welcoming the “Peru” hit maker to the ‘Spark family’, the phone brand wrote: “FIRE et SPARK. Welcome the one and only @fireboydml to the #SPARK family – The SPARK AMBASSADOR.”   Social media comedienne Madam Social dies     I’ll relocate to Ghana if Atiku or Tinubu becomes…     Why I’m never getting married, by Timaya   The excited 26-year-old singer, also proudly took to the photo and video sharing app to share the news with his fans. “Proud and excited to be part of this lit geng, TECNO! Can’t wait to show off the best of my selfies with the latest SPARK Series. Head over to @tecnomobileng to support my new family!”, he wrote